  "calculateur-inflation-fr": "Scénario privé d'inflation sourcé. Demandez montant, devise, taux annuel, période, source et date récente. Ne fournissez aucun taux pays, flux CPI en direct, multiplicateur de panier, prévision ou conseil d'investissement et n'envoyez aucune valeur financière à une IA. Structured inflation scenario contract: amount, currency, annual inflation rate, period, source label and recent checked date are supplied by the user and calculated locally. The rate must have been checked within 365 days and remains constant for the scenario. The result is not a forecast and does not represent every household or product basket. No country rate, live CPI feed, basket multiplier, investment recommendation, AI prefill or network request is supplied. Source: Inflation Scenario Calculator user-input methodology with World Bank CPI indicator metadata context. Reviewed: 2026-07-22.",
